				</p>

				<h4 id="f++-eg">
					f++ example
				</h4>
				<p>
					Examples of <mono>bool</mono> being defined with <mono>f++</mono>:					

<div align="center" style="margin-top:-10px; margin-bottom:10px">
<pre class="prettyprint inline linenums lang-nift">
std::bool a=0, b=1
std::bool(x, y, z)
:=(std::bool, finished = 0)</pre>
</div>
				</p>

				<h4 id="n++-eg">
					n++ example
				</h4>
